{"tid":946264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"每年稅收6.8億美元 紐約州長：明年起積極推動大麻合法化","createTime":"2018-12-18T11:56:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T12:13:19.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"585aa6c30527d0bb228ce59577bff7107bafdc9b","tid":946264,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T11:56:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpYTiaF2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpYTiaF2.jpg&h=71aa3fd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國紐約州州長科莫（Andrew Cuomo）昨日正式宣布，明年將積極推動娛樂用大麻合法化。（路透）<br />\n<br />\n2018-12-18 14:40<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國紐約州州長科莫（Andrew Cuomo）昨（17）日正式宣布，明年將積極推動娛樂用大麻合法化，認為大麻所帶來的收益與優點超過弊端，除了每年可高達新台幣200億元的稅收，更有助改善刑事犯人族裔失衡問題。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，科莫上個月第三度成功連任州長後，昨日宣佈明年的百日施政大綱，表示重點將為推動娛樂用大麻合法化，強調隨時代變遷，紐約需要跟上其他州的合法化腳步。科莫認為，大麻全面合法是解決長期以來，美國對非洲裔美國人和少數族群的不平等對待。「我們必須要終結不必要且不公正的刑事定罪」。<br />\n<br />\n據紐約州政府計算，大麻合法化後市場規模約可達17到35億美元（約新台幣510～1050億元），估計稅收可達2.5～6.8億美元（約新台幣70～204億元），未來將用於提升紐約州的公共交通基礎建設。<br />\n☆少一份毒品就多一份健康，自由時報提醒您遠離毒品☆<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2645802\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2645802&d=KjSuXlltxR9UwDlHfjOcBDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=acf7a98b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2645802&h=69bc2050\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2645802</a>"},{"pid":"02938cab9384c8a8e868a5ae4486540cba560ba3","tid":946264,"uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T12:08:13.000Z","msg":"逐漸Dystopia化<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2c05efa085dc8c4ecc13a6f05f5286f8551ef0c","tid":946264,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T12:10:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">更有助改善刑事犯人族裔失衡問題。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ce7ad3bf8390dbac759f0c6c6e30246faffa8c","tid":946264,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T12:13:19.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過強姦合法化都可以增加勞動人口？"}]}